                    "created": "2011-02-18T11:21:09.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-02-18T11:21:09.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/44495",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kingcrunch",
                        "name": "kingcrunch",
                        "displayName": "Sebastian Krebs",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thats now a really long time ago and today I cant remember what I tried at that time. I cant imagine really useful use-cases nowadays. However, its possible at least in SQLite and I also can imagine, that there are use cases ;)\r\n\r\nSo, for me its not significant anymore.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=kingcrunch",
                        "name": "kingcrunch",
                        "displayName": "Sebastian Krebs",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-02-18T12:56:38.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-02-18T12:56:38.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/48587",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jhuet",
                        "name": "jhuet",
                        "displayName": "J\u00e9r\u00e9my Huet",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nThe bug still remains. A NULL field in a PK is possible on most databases but the method find() can't retrieve it for the reasons Sebastian gave.\r\n\r\nThe case we're having is a NULLable datetime field that is part of the composite PK.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=jhuet",
                        "name": "jhuet",
                        "displayName": "J\u00e9r\u00e9my Huet",
